{"tid":1498931,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［反洗腦文宣］藍絲長輩最愛 垃圾洗腦片","createTime":"2019-08-23T14:29:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T16:40:32.000Z","uid":270766,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"12e85a1c904972a3d3e0ac614e25db1cd9645e64","tid":1498931,"uid":270766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:29:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_Xyr26qAJ8g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_Xyr26qAJ8g&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlApnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=35c7beef\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_Xyr26qAJ8g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">想法源於我接觸到既藍絲長輩<br />\n經常睇果D大陸分析局勢果D洗腦片<br />\n好多講經濟, 講國與國之間關係, 講陰謀<br />\n好似好專業咁既分析片<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n洗腦片定律=普通話+簡體字幕+slide show</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n所以有呢個以其人之道既想法，<br />\n所以，第一段片係朋友協助下誕生了！<br />\n內容係用網上轉載一位律師嘅心聲，入邊所有相同片都係網上面搵嘅<br />\n低成本, 低要求, 唔完美可接受但需要改善改進, <br />\n唔知成效會如何, 請幫手share, 祝工作順利, 生活愉快!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>forward條片出去，感動更多藍絲！<br />\n好快有vol.2</strong></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[藍絲洗腦]極需要普通話專業分析文宣!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1434845</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"02c5bcf2fdeeb5ebf7721e59053959aa02c217e5","tid":1498931,"uid":270766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:32:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"534ddb2adb89c46b925b03c04cadcf23c07eb770","tid":1498931,"uid":111982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:32:38.000Z","msg":"824 早機晏觀一日遊"},{"pid":"7